{"ec":"ET00000345","t":"Athidhi","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/athidhi-et00000345-1779358611.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/athidhi-et00000345-1779358611.jpg","d":"Athidhi (Guest) is an orphan adopted by a couple, whose murder he is later implicated for, giving him a jail time of 13 years.<br/><br/>When Athidhi comes out of jail, his only ambition is to kill Kaiser, the psychopath who killed the couple. The romantic element is contributed by the couple`s daughter, Amrita, who has also been hating Athidhi ever since and blames him for her parent`s death.","rd":"2007-10-18","rt":172,"ct":"A","g":["Action","Crime","Romantic"],"l":["Telugu"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Mahesh Babu","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/mahesh-babu-36982-20-12-2017-04-21-05.jpg"],["Amrita Rao","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/amrita-rao-146-18-01-2019-12-43-22.jpg"],["Murli Sharma","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/murli-sharma-1530-24-03-2017-18-02-07.jpg"],["Venu Madhav","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/venu-madhav-4097-26-09-2019-05-16-35.jpg"],["Kota Srinivasa Rao","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/kota-srinivasa-rao-3597-24-03-2017-18-02-13.jpg"],["Nassar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/nassar-8386-1657383113.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Surender","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/surender-iein004560-24-03-2017-12-58-46.jpg"],["Surender Reddy","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/surender-reddy-11826-24-03-2017-17-46-44.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[["Mani Sharma","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/mani-sharma-1353-1752144963.jpg"]],"c":[["Sameera Reddy","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/ie